reviewText: 3 of 4 tapes came with head covers broken off. Had to take head covers off blank tapes and replace but tapes still don't play well...too much trouble to return. Oh well

This is quality childrens entertainment packaged in a nice box set, factory wrapped. 2 Copies available on the Amazon Marketplace starting at $14.99. This box set was released in 1992. Fully animated fun for kids.
